## Data Pipeline Architecture

```
[ WAF Access Logs ]
[ EC2 App Logs   ]  ──►  [ Kinesis Data Stream ]  ──►  [ Lambda (Person 3) ]
[ RDS Query Logs ]              │                               │
                                │                          [ SNS Alert ]
                                ▼
                      [ Kinesis Firehose ]
                                │
                    ┌───────────┼───────────┐
                    ▼           ▼           ▼
                [ S3 Bucket ] [ CloudWatch ] [ Athena ]
                (Archive)     (Dashboard)   (Forensics)
```

