## CloudWatch Alarm Configuration

| Alarm | Metric | Threshold | Action |
|-------|--------|-----------|--------|
| High attack rate | `WafBlockedRequests` | > 50/min | Notify SNS |
| Lambda errors | `Lambda/Errors` | > 5/min | Notify SNS |
| Kinesis throttling | `Kinesis/WriteProvisionedThroughputExceeded` | > 0 | Add shards |

